org.openimaj.content.animation.animator

Class LongArrayValueAnimator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.content.animation.animator.LongArrayValueAnimator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ValueAnimator<long[]>

    public class LongArrayValueAnimator
extends Object
implements ValueAnimator<long[]>
    A ValueAnimator capable of producing long arrays from a set of potentially independent underlying ValueAnimators.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
